        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat(telegram): non-streaming tool+commentary progress accumulator",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Add a mode-independent tool+commentary event accumulator in the Telegram dispatcher\n- Collects `onToolStart` and `onItemEvent(preamble)` events into a `persistedProgressLog` regardless of streaming mode\n- On final delivery, prepends the chronological log above the answer with a `---` divider\n- Respects Telegram's 4096 char limit by truncating oldest entries\n\n## Motivation\n\nWhen streaming is off (`streamMode: \"off\"`) or reasoning forces block mode (`reasoningLevel: \"on\"`), no draft streams are created. The compositor from #89850 is inactive (`active: false`), so tool/commentary events are silently discarded. This PR fills that gap.\n\nDepends on #89850 (persist mode config flag). Pairs with #89834 (Claude CLI commentary events).\n\n## Files changed\n\n- `extensions/telegram/src/bot-message-dispatch.ts` -- accumulator + prepend to final delivery\n- `src/config/types.base.ts` -- `persistProgress` field (shared with #89850)\n- `src/config/zod-schema.providers-core.ts` -- schema entry (shared with #89850)\n- `src/channels/streaming.ts` -- `resolveChannelStreamingProgressPersist` resolver (shared with #89850)\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [ ] Non-streaming mode with persistProgress: tool events accumulated, prepended to final answer\n- [ ] Streaming mode with persistProgress: accumulator collects alongside compositor\n- [ ] Without persistProgress: no accumulation\n",
        "branch": "feat/non-streaming-tool-progress-accumulator",
